    "description": "<strong>From little seeds grow big forrests! </strong>Plant trees, spread your roots and explore the underground in this cute and relaxing small-town sim. Use the forest to improve the life of your neighbours, find hidden treasures underground and collect tons of trees and animals from around the world!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GROW</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319400/extras/3081eb5b90bddaeec1de2c27af0f55b5.poster.avif?t=1679260588\" width=654 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319400/extras/3081eb5b90bddaeec1de2c27af0f55b5.webm?t=1679260588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319400/extras/3081eb5b90bddaeec1de2c27af0f55b5.mp4?t=1679260588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Find a good patch of soil and sprout! Select the right tree for the job and explore the underground, collecting water, minerals and fossils along the way.<br>You could even clean up the soil from nasty pollutants while you're down there!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HARVEST</h2>Cut your trees to get wood, or let them grow and wait for fruits! Use the ecosystem to your advantage and improve your harvests day after day!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >IMPROVE</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319400/extras/a15279f4288c907dce75bebb70af19de.poster.avif?t=1679260588\" width=654 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319400/extras/a15279f4288c907dce75bebb70af19de.webm?t=1679260588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319400/extras/a15279f4288c907dce75bebb70af19de.mp4?t=1679260588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use your forrest to better the lives of your animal neighbours! Grow your town, unlock new building and activities, talk to your fellow townsfolk and try to help them!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TRAVEL</h2>Travel to different biomes with unique challenges (arid desert, frozen mountain, polluted city...) and discover unique new trees and animals!",
